INSERT INTO appraisal_market_price(
                    is_buy,
                    appraisal_id,
                    type_id,

                    min,
                    max,
                    avg,
                    total_orders
                )
                SELECT true, $1, * FROM UNNEST(
                    $2::INTEGER[],
                    $3::DOUBLE PRECISION[],
                    $4::DOUBLE PRECISION[],
                    $5::DOUBLE PRECISION[],
                    $6::BIGINT[]
                )
                RETURNING id
